{"tid":719061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ｊｏｊｏ　STAND】62歲傷者今午不治 槍擊案增至兩死計時引爆","createTime":"2018-06-27T07:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T07:54:26.000Z","uid":65346,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ffe27ceb0b2e29b1be8b5772ba972c39b0049ced","tid":719061,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:12:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180627/58368762\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180627%2F58368762&d=q%2F0ocy0U8FGeelLTiruMvL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=369fd630\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180627%2F58368762&h=a7c0cce9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180627/58368762</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【14:55】62歲傷者搶救無效不治<br />\n<br />\n太古城鰂魚涌公園昨日發生爭產開槍殺人案，女保鑣涉嫌槍擊兩舅父和兩阿姨，造成一死三傷(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2lyuxpI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2lyuxpI&d=q%2F0ocy0U8FGeelLTiruMvL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=328c6684\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2lyuxpI</a>)。女疑犯仍然被警方扣留調查。案中被槍殺及受傷的全部是疑犯母親的弟妹，分別是現年80歲的大姨少芬、72歲大舅父前駒、62歲細舅父鎮基及60歲細姨小慧。其中大姨少芬頭部中槍，後腦前額被子彈射穿，送院搶救後不治。<br />\n細舅父鎮基頭、手及肺受傷，搶救情況一直危殆，延至今午不治；大舅父左上臂中槍，送院時危殆，至今早情況有好轉，由危殆轉為嚴重；細姨左上臂中槍，清醒送院，經搶救後穩定。"},{"pid":"903318577f202d36375301c64638deca5e351062","tid":719061,"uid":83328,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:14:11.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢Jo Jo Stand<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41b1413c0d46cd7f50dbba544c695965225008c","tid":719061,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.rimg.com.tw/s2/c/6d/20/21640873229600_713_m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.rimg.com.tw%2Fs2%2Fc%2F6d%2F20%2F21640873229600_713_m.jpg&h=08f0b77c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n奇妙冒險 第五部 米斯達 性感手槍"},{"pid":"da0da4b1537f90441ae5866a4e94bfc720ae869e","tid":719061,"uid":49275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:14:46.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc3730d3873d92984f6c33588e3bc61b69f9912d","tid":719061,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:15:07.000Z","msg":"剩下２件 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4899a2a11434ef101c628dba96aa8e34b7669a7b","tid":719061,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:15:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>後腦前額被子彈射穿，送院搶救後不治。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n後入前出<br />\n<br />\n想轉身逃走, 但都被後射"},{"pid":"c9a8860ee34101716cc6ecd030a3534c62d17394","tid":719061,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc3730d3873d92984f6c33588e3bc61b69f9912d","tid":719061,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:15:07.000Z","msg":"剩下２件 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:16:22.000Z","msg":"另兩個手臂中, <br />\n<br />\n應該唔會死得"},{"pid":"8e78dd7df4fec3a0b81c637e264dad08089b0dda","tid":719061,"uid":171758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:16:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb3cee44fe91b9eeecee1089c8280269b638a95c","tid":719061,"uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c9a8860ee34101716cc6ecd030a3534c62d17394","